  "title": "MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Plattering Co. Pte Ltd</strong>, known for its beautiful grazing tables and creative catering buffet setup displays, sharing platters, bowls and bentos and unique catering setups. As we continue to expand, we are seeking for a skilled and efficient <strong>Operations Manager</strong>  to join our catering team. The Operations Manager is responsible for overseeing the daily logistics and operational functions of the catering service. This role ensures that all food orders are accurately fulfilled, deliveries are executed on time, and customers receive exceptional service. The Operations Manager coordinates team schedules, manages drivers, and serves as a key point of contact for customer enquiries and complaints.</p><h2><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h2>",
